{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "黄帝"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "兴起与征讨"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "1",
      "note": "n1",
      "html": "<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1\"><span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>者，</span><span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1b\"><span class=\"person\">少典</span>之子，</span>姓<span class=\"person\">公孙</span>，名曰<span class=\"person\">轩辕</span>。<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1c\">生而<span class=\"mythical\">神灵</span>，</span>弱而能言，幼而徇齐，长而敦敏，成而聪明。"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c1",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c1a",
        "html": "<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1_1a\"><span class=\"clan\">神农氏</span>世衰。</span><span class=\"official\">诸侯</span>相侵伐，暴虐百姓，而<span class=\"clan\">神农氏</span>弗能征。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c1b",
        "from": "c1a",
        "html": "於是<span class=\"person\">轩辕</span>乃习用<span class=\"artifact\">干戈</span>，以征不享，诸侯咸来宾从。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c2",
      "id": "1.1",
      "indent": true,
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c2a",
        "html": "而<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1_1b\"><span class=\"person\">蚩尤</span>最为暴，</span>莫能伐。<span class=\"person\">炎帝</span>欲侵陵诸侯，诸侯咸归<span class=\"person\">轩辕</span>。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c2b",
        "from": "c2a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">轩辕</span>乃修德振兵，治五气，蓺五种，抚万民，度四方，教<span class=\"biology\">熊</span><span class=\"biology\">罴</span><span class=\"biology\">貔貅</span><span class=\"biology\">貙</span><span class=\"biology\">虎</span>，以与<span class=\"person\">炎帝</span>战於<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1_1c\"><span class=\"place\">阪泉之野</span></span>。三战，然後得其志。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c3",
      "id": "1.2",
      "indent": true,
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c3a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">蚩尤</span>作乱，不用帝命。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c3b",
        "from": "c3a",
        "html": "於是<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>乃徵师诸侯，与<span class=\"person\">蚩尤</span>战於<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n1_2a\"><span class=\"place\">涿鹿之野</span></span>，遂禽杀<span class=\"person\">蚩尤</span>。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c4",
      "id": "1.3",
      "indent": true,
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c4a",
        "html": "而诸侯咸尊<span class=\"person\">轩辕</span>为<span class=\"official\">天子</span>，代<span class=\"clan\">神农氏</span>，是为<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c4b",
        "from": "c4a",
        "html": "<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>有不顺者，<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>从而征之，平者去之，披山通道，未尝宁居。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "疆域与治理"
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "id": "2",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "东至于<span class=\"place\">海</span>，登<span class=\"place\">丸山</span>，及<span class=\"place\">岱宗</span>。",
        "西至于<span class=\"place\">空桐</span>，登<span class=\"place\">鸡头</span>。",
        "南至于<span class=\"place\">江</span>，登<span class=\"place\">熊</span>、<span class=\"place\">湘</span>。",
        "北逐<span class=\"tribe\">荤粥</span>，合符<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n2a\"><span class=\"place\">釜山</span></span>，而邑于<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n2b\"><span class=\"place\">涿鹿之阿</span></span>。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "3",
      "html": "迁徙往来无常处，以师兵为营卫。官名皆以云命，为<span class=\"official\">云师</span>。置<span class=\"official\">左右大监</span>，监于万国。万国和，而<span class=\"mythical\">鬼神</span><span class=\"place\">山川</span><span class=\"concept\">封禅</span>与为多焉。获<span class=\"artifact\">宝鼎</span>，迎日推筴。举<span class=\"person\">风后</span>、<span class=\"person\">力牧</span>、<span class=\"person\">常先</span>、<span class=\"person\">大鸿</span>以治民。顺<span class=\"celestial\">天地</span>之纪，幽明之占，死生之说，存亡之难。时播<span class=\"biology\">百穀</span><span class=\"biology\">草木</span>，淳化<span class=\"biology\">鸟兽</span><span class=\"biology\">蟲蛾</span>，旁罗<span class=\"celestial\">日月星辰</span>水波土石<span class=\"artifact\">金玉</span>，劳勤心力耳目，节用水火材物。有<span class=\"concept\">土德</span>之瑞，故号<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "4",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>二十五子，其得姓者十四人。"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "后裔与世系"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "4.1",
      "note": "n4_1",
      "html": "<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n4_1\"><span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>居<span class=\"place\">轩辕之丘</span>，</span>而娶於<span class=\"place\">西陵</span>之女，是为<span class=\"person\">嫘祖</span>。<span class=\"person\">嫘祖</span>为<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>正妃，生二子，其後皆有<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>："
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "其一曰<span class=\"person\">玄嚣</span>，是为<span class=\"person\">青阳</span>，<span class=\"person\">青阳</span>降居<span class=\"place\">江水</span>；",
        "其二曰<span class=\"person\">昌意</span>，降居<span class=\"place\">若水</span>。<span class=\"person\">昌意</span>娶<span class=\"clan\">蜀山氏</span>女，曰<span class=\"person\">昌仆</span>，生<span class=\"person\">高阳</span>，<span class=\"person\">高阳</span>有<span class=\"concept\">圣德</span>焉。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c5",
      "id": "4.2",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c5a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>崩，葬<span class=\"place\">桥山</span>。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c5b",
        "from": "c5a",
        "html": "其孙<span class=\"person\">昌意</span>之子<span class=\"person\">高阳</span>立，是为<span class=\"person\">帝颛顼</span>也。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "hr"
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "帝颛顼"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "5",
      "note": "n5",
      "html": "<span class=\"note-anchor\" data-note=\"n5\"><span class=\"person\">帝颛顼高阳</span>者，<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>之孙而<span class=\"person\">昌意</span>之子也。</span>静渊以有谋，疏通而知事；养材以任地，载时以象天，依<span class=\"mythical\">鬼神</span>以制义，治气以教化，絜诚以<span class=\"concept\">祭祀</span>。"
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "北至于<span class=\"place\">幽陵</span>，",
        "南至于<span class=\"place\">交阯</span>，",
        "西至于<span class=\"place\">流沙</span>，",
        "东至于<span class=\"place\">蟠木</span>。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "5.1",
      "indent": true,
      "html": "<span class=\"concept\">动静</span>之物，大小之神，<span class=\"concept\">日月</span>所照，莫不砥属。"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c6",
      "id": "6",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c6a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">帝颛顼</span>生子曰<span class=\"person\">穷蝉</span>。<span class=\"person\">颛顼</span>崩，"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c6b",
        "from": "c6a",
        "html": "而<span class=\"person\">玄嚣</span>之孙<span class=\"person\">高辛</span>立，是为<span class=\"person\">帝喾</span>。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "hr"
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "帝喾"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "7",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">帝喾高辛</span>者，<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>之曾孙也。<span class=\"person\">高辛</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">蟜极</span>，<span class=\"person\">蟜极</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">玄嚣</span>，<span class=\"person\">玄嚣</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>。自<span class=\"person\">玄嚣</span>与<span class=\"person\">蟜极</span>皆不得在位，至<span class=\"person\">高辛</span>即帝位。<span class=\"person\">高辛</span>於<span class=\"person\">颛顼</span>为族子。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "8",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">高辛</span>生而<span class=\"mythical\">神灵</span>，自言其名。普施利物，不於其身。聪以知远，明以察微。顺天之义，知民之急。仁而威，惠而信，脩身而<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>服。"
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "取地之财而节用之，",
        "抚教万民而利诲之，",
        "历<span class=\"concept\">日月</span>而迎送之，",
        "明<span class=\"mythical\">鬼神</span>而敬事之。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "8.1",
      "indent": true,
      "html": "其色郁郁，其德嶷嶷。其动也时，其服也<span class=\"official\">士</span>。<span class=\"person\">帝喾</span>溉执中而遍<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>，<span class=\"concept\">日月</span>所照，风雨所至，莫不从服。"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c7",
      "id": "9",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c7a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">帝喾</span>娶<span class=\"clan\">陈锋氏</span>女，生<span class=\"person\">放勋</span>。娶<span class=\"clan\">娵訾氏</span>女，生<span class=\"person\">挚</span>。<span class=\"person\">帝喾</span>崩，而<span class=\"person\">挚</span>代立。<span class=\"person\">帝挚</span>立，不善，"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c7b",
        "from": "c7a",
        "html": "而弟<span class=\"person\">放勋</span>立，是为<span class=\"person\">帝尧</span>。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "hr"
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "帝尧"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "钦明文思"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "10",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">帝尧</span>者，<span class=\"person\">放勋</span>。其仁如天，其知如神。就之如日，望之如云。富而不骄，贵而不舒。黄收纯衣，彤车乘<span class=\"place\">白马</span>。能明驯德，以亲九族。九族既睦，便章百姓。百姓<span class=\"person\">昭明</span>，合和万国。"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "历法与农时"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "11",
      "html": "乃命<span class=\"person\">羲</span>、<span class=\"person\">和</span>，敬顺<span class=\"place\">昊天</span>，数法<span class=\"celestial\">日月星辰</span>，敬授民时。"
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "[11.1] 分命<span class=\"person\">羲仲</span>，居<span class=\"place\">郁夷</span>，曰<span class=\"place\">旸谷</span>。敬道日出，便程东作。<span class=\"celestial\">日中</span>，<span class=\"celestial\">星鸟</span>，以殷<span class=\"celestial\">中春</span>。其民析，<span class=\"biology\">鸟兽</span>字微。",
        "[11.2] 申命<span class=\"person\">羲叔</span>，居<span class=\"place\">南交</span>。便程南为，敬致。<span class=\"celestial\">日永</span>，<span class=\"celestial\">星火</span>，以正<span class=\"celestial\">中夏</span>。其民因，<span class=\"biology\">鸟兽</span>希革。",
        "[11.3] 申命<span class=\"person\">和仲</span>，居<span class=\"place\">西土</span>，曰<span class=\"place\">昧谷</span>。敬道日入，便程西成。<span class=\"celestial\">夜中</span>，<span class=\"celestial\">星虚</span>，以正<span class=\"celestial\">中秋</span>。其民夷易，<span class=\"biology\">鸟兽</span>毛毨。",
        "[11.4] 申命<span class=\"person\">和叔</span>；居<span class=\"place\">北方</span>，曰<span class=\"place\">幽都</span>。便在伏物。<span class=\"celestial\">日短</span>，<span class=\"celestial\">星昴</span>，以正<span class=\"celestial\">中冬</span>。其民燠，<span class=\"biology\">鸟兽</span>氄毛。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "11.5",
      "html": "岁三百六<span class=\"timeref\">十六日</span>，以<span class=\"celestial\">闰月</span>正<span class=\"timeref\">四时</span>。信饬百官，众功皆兴。"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "禅让之始"
    },
    {
      "t": "dialogue",
      "id": "12",
      "indent": true,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "12.1",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「谁可顺此事？」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.2",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">放齐</span>曰：「嗣子<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>开明。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.3",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「吁！顽凶，不用。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.4",
          "html": "尧又曰：「谁可者？」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.5",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">讙兜</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">共工</span>旁聚布功，可用。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.6",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">共工</span>善言，其用僻，似恭漫天，不可。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.7",
          "html": "尧又曰：「嗟，<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>，汤汤洪水滔天，浩浩怀山<span class=\"place\">襄陵</span>，下民其忧，有能使治者？」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.8",
          "html": "皆曰<span class=\"person\">鲧</span>可。"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.9",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">鲧</span>负命毁族，不可。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.10",
          "html": "<span class=\"official\">岳</span>曰：「异哉，试不可用而已。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "12.11",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>於是听岳用<span class=\"person\">鲧</span>。<span class=\"timeref\">九岁</span>，功用不成。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "dialogue",
      "id": "13",
      "indent": true,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "13.1",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「嗟！<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>：朕在位七十载，汝能庸命，践朕位？」"
        },
        {
          "id": "13.2",
          "html": "<span class=\"official\">岳</span>应曰：「鄙德忝帝位。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "13.3",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「悉举贵戚及疏远隐匿者。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "13.4",
          "html": "众皆言於<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「有矜在民间，曰<span class=\"person\">虞舜</span>。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "13.5",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「然，朕闻之。其何如？」"
        },
        {
          "id": "13.6",
          "html": "<span class=\"official\">岳</span>曰：「盲者子。父顽，母嚚，弟傲，能和以孝，烝烝治，不至奸。」"
        },
        {
          "id": "13.7",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰：「吾其试哉。」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "13.8",
      "html": "於是尧妻之二女，观其德於二女。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>饬下二女於<span class=\"place\">妫汭</span>，如妇礼。尧善之，乃使<span class=\"person\">舜</span>慎和<span class=\"concept\">五典</span>，<span class=\"concept\">五典</span>能从。乃遍入百官，百官时序。宾於四门，四门穆穆，诸侯远方宾客皆敬。<span class=\"person\">尧</span>使<span class=\"person\">舜</span>入山林川泽，暴<span class=\"artifact\">风雷</span>雨，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>行不迷。<span class=\"person\">尧</span>以为圣，召<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「女谋事至而言可绩，<span class=\"timeref\">三年</span>矣。女登帝位。」<span class=\"person\">舜</span>让於德不怿。<span class=\"timeref\">正月上日</span>，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>受终於<span class=\"place\">文祖</span>。<span class=\"place\">文祖</span>者，尧大祖也。"
    },
    {
      "t": "hr"
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "帝舜"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "摄政与礼法"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "14",
      "html": "於是<span class=\"person\">帝尧</span>老，命<span class=\"person\">舜</span>摄行<span class=\"official\">天子</span>之政，以观<span class=\"concept\">天命</span>。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>乃在<span class=\"artifact\">璿玑玉衡</span>，以齐<span class=\"celestial\">七政</span>。遂类于<span class=\"mythical\">上帝</span>，禋于<span class=\"concept\">六宗</span>，望于<span class=\"place\">山川</span>，辩于群神。揖<span class=\"artifact\">五瑞</span>，择吉月日，见<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>诸牧，班瑞。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "14.1",
      "html": "<span class=\"timeref\">岁二月</span>，东<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>，至於<span class=\"place\">岱宗</span>，祡，望秩於<span class=\"place\">山川</span>。遂见<span class=\"place\">东方</span><span class=\"official\">君长</span>，合时月正日，同律度量衡，脩<span class=\"concept\">五礼</span>五玉三帛二生一死为<span class=\"person\">挚</span>，如<span class=\"artifact\">五器</span>，卒乃复。<span class=\"timeref\">五月</span>，南<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>；<span class=\"timeref\">八月</span>，西<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>；<span class=\"timeref\">十一月</span>，北<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>：皆如初。归，至于祖祢庙，用<span class=\"biology\">特牛</span>礼。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "14.2",
      "html": "<span class=\"timeref\">五岁</span>一<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>，群后四朝。遍告以言，明试以功，车服以庸。肇十有二州，决川。象以<span class=\"concept\">典刑</span>，<span class=\"concept\">流宥五刑</span>，鞭作<span class=\"concept\">官刑</span>，扑作<span class=\"concept\">教刑</span>，金作<span class=\"concept\">赎刑</span>。眚灾过，赦；怙终贼，刑。钦哉，钦哉，惟刑之静哉！"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "惩办四罪"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c8",
      "id": "15",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c8a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">讙兜</span>进言<span class=\"person\">共工</span>，<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰不可而试之<span class=\"official\">工师</span>，<span class=\"person\">共工</span>果淫辟。<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>举<span class=\"person\">鲧</span>治鸿水，<span class=\"person\">尧</span>以为不可，<span class=\"official\">岳</span>彊请试之，试之而无功，故百姓不便。<span class=\"tribe\">三苗</span>在<span class=\"place\">江淮</span>、<span class=\"place\">荆州</span>数为乱。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c8b",
        "from": "c8a",
        "html": "於是<span class=\"person\">舜</span>归而言於帝，"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "[15.1] 请流<span class=\"person\">共工</span>於<span class=\"place\">幽陵</span>，以变<span class=\"tribe\">北狄</span>；",
        "[15.2] 放<span class=\"person\">驩兜</span>於<span class=\"place\">崇山</span>，以变<span class=\"tribe\">南蛮</span>；",
        "[15.3] 迁<span class=\"tribe\">三苗</span>於<span class=\"place\">三危</span>，以变<span class=\"tribe\">西戎</span>；",
        "[15.4] 殛<span class=\"person\">鲧</span>於<span class=\"place\">羽山</span>，以变<span class=\"tribe\">东夷</span>："
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "summary",
      "rid": "s1",
      "from": "c8b",
      "id": "15.5",
      "anchor": "head",
      "html": "四罪而<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>咸服。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "16",
      "html": "尧立<span class=\"timeref\">七十年</span>得<span class=\"person\">舜</span>，<span class=\"timeref\">二十年</span>而老，令<span class=\"person\">舜</span>摄行<span class=\"official\">天子</span>之政，荐之於天。尧辟位凡<span class=\"timeref\">二十八年</span>而崩。百姓悲哀，如丧父母。<span class=\"timeref\">三年</span>，四方莫举乐，以思尧。"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c9",
      "id": "16.1",
      "indent": true,
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c9a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>知子<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>之不肖，不足授<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>，"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c9b",
        "from": "c9a",
        "html": "於是乃权授<span class=\"person\">舜</span>。授<span class=\"person\">舜</span>，则<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>得其利而<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>病；授<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>，则<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>病而<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>得其利。<span class=\"person\">尧</span>曰「终不以<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>之病而利一人」，而卒授<span class=\"person\">舜</span>以<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c10",
      "id": "16.2",
      "indent": true,
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c10a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>崩，<span class=\"timeref\">三年</span>之丧毕，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>让辟<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>於<span class=\"place\">南河之南</span>。诸侯<span class=\"action\">朝觐</span>者不之<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>而之<span class=\"person\">舜</span>，狱讼者不之<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>而之<span class=\"person\">舜</span>，讴歌者不讴歌<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>而讴歌<span class=\"person\">舜</span>。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c10b",
        "from": "c10a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰「天也」，夫而後之<span class=\"place\">中国</span>践<span class=\"official\">天子</span>位焉，是为<span class=\"person\">帝舜</span>。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "德行与磨难"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "17",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">虞舜</span>者，名曰<span class=\"person\">重华</span>。<span class=\"person\">重华</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>，<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">桥牛</span>，<span class=\"person\">桥牛</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">句望</span>，<span class=\"person\">句望</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">敬康</span>，<span class=\"person\">敬康</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">穷蝉</span>，<span class=\"person\">穷蝉</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">帝颛顼</span>，<span class=\"person\">颛顼</span>父曰<span class=\"person\">昌意</span>：以至<span class=\"person\">舜</span><span class=\"timeref\">七世</span>矣。自从<span class=\"person\">穷蝉</span>以至<span class=\"person\">帝舜</span>，皆微为庶人。"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c11",
      "id": "18",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c11a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>父<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>盲，而<span class=\"person\">舜</span>母死，<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>更娶妻而生<span class=\"person\">象</span>，<span class=\"person\">象</span>傲。<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>爱後妻子，常欲杀<span class=\"person\">舜</span>，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>避逃；及有小过，则受罪。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c11b",
        "from": "c11a",
        "html": "顺事父及後母与弟，日以笃谨，匪有解。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "19",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>，<span class=\"place\">冀州</span>之人也。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>耕<span class=\"place\">历山</span>，渔<span class=\"place\">雷泽</span>，陶<span class=\"place\">河滨</span>，作什器於<span class=\"place\">寿丘</span>，就时於<span class=\"place\">负夏</span>。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>父<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>顽，母嚚，弟<span class=\"person\">象</span>傲，皆欲杀<span class=\"person\">舜</span>。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>顺適不失子道，兄弟孝慈。欲杀，不可得；即求，尝在侧。"
    },
    {
      "t": "block",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "t": "p",
          "id": "20",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span><span class=\"timeref\">年二十</span>以孝闻。三十而<span class=\"person\">帝尧</span>问可用者，<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>咸荐<span class=\"person\">虞舜</span>，曰可。於是<span class=\"person\">尧</span>乃以二女妻<span class=\"person\">舜</span>以观其内，使九男与处以观其外。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>居<span class=\"place\">妫汭</span>，内行弥谨。尧二女不敢以贵骄事<span class=\"person\">舜</span>亲戚，甚有妇道。尧九男皆益笃。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>耕<span class=\"place\">历山</span>，<span class=\"place\">历山</span>之人皆让畔；渔<span class=\"place\">雷泽</span>，<span class=\"place\">雷泽</span>上人皆让居；陶<span class=\"place\">河滨</span>，<span class=\"place\">河滨</span>器皆不苦窳。<span class=\"timeref\">一年</span>而所居成聚，<span class=\"timeref\">二年</span>成邑，<span class=\"timeref\">三年</span><span class=\"place\">成都</span>。<span class=\"person\">尧</span>乃赐<span class=\"person\">舜</span>絺衣，与琴，为筑仓廪，予<span class=\"biology\">牛羊</span>。"
        },
        {
          "t": "causal",
          "rid": "c12",
          "id": "20.1",
          "indent": true,
          "cause": {
            "rid": "c12a",
            "html": "<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>尚复欲杀之，使<span class=\"person\">舜</span>上涂廪，<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>从下纵火焚廪。"
          },
          "effect": {
            "rid": "c12b",
            "from": "c12a",
            "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>乃以两笠自扞而下，去，得不死。"
          }
        },
        {
          "t": "causal",
          "rid": "c13",
          "id": "20.2",
          "indent": true,
          "cause": {
            "rid": "c13a",
            "html": "後<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>又使<span class=\"person\">舜</span>穿井，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>穿井为匿空旁出。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>既入深，<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>与<span class=\"person\">象</span>共下土实井，"
          },
          "effect": {
            "rid": "c13b",
            "from": "c13a",
            "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>从匿空出，去。<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>、象喜，以<span class=\"person\">舜</span>为已死。"
          }
        },
        {
          "t": "dialogue",
          "id": "20.2d",
          "indent": true,
          "lines": [
            {
              "id": "20.2d.1",
              "html": "<span class=\"person\">象</span>曰「本谋者象。」"
            },
            {
              "id": "20.2d.2",
              "html": "<span class=\"person\">象</span>与其父母分，於是曰：「<span class=\"person\">舜</span>妻尧二女，与琴，象取之。<span class=\"biology\">牛羊</span>仓廪予父母。」"
            },
            {
              "id": "20.2d.3",
              "html": "象乃止<span class=\"person\">舜</span>宫居，鼓其琴。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>往见之。"
            },
            {
              "id": "20.2d.4",
              "html": "<span class=\"person\">象</span>鄂不怿，曰：「我思<span class=\"person\">舜</span>正郁陶！」"
            },
            {
              "id": "20.2d.5",
              "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「然，尔其庶矣！」"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "id": "20.3",
          "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>复事<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>爱弟弥谨。於是<span class=\"person\">尧</span>乃试<span class=\"person\">舜</span><span class=\"concept\">五典</span>百官，皆治。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "举贤任能"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "举贤任能"
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c14",
      "id": "21",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c14a",
        "html": "昔<span class=\"clan\">高阳氏</span>有才子八人，世得其利，谓之「<span class=\"person\">八恺</span>」。<span class=\"clan\">高辛氏</span>有才子八人，世谓之「<span class=\"person\">八元</span>」。此十六族者，世济其美，不陨其名。至於<span class=\"person\">尧</span>，尧未能举。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c14b",
        "from": "c14a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>举<span class=\"person\">八恺</span>，使主后土，以揆百事，莫不时序。举<span class=\"person\">八元</span>，使布<span class=\"concept\">五教</span>于四方，父义，母慈，兄友，弟恭，子孝，内平外成。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "id": "22",
      "items": [
        "[22.1] 昔<span class=\"clan\">帝鸿氏</span>有不才子，掩义隐贼，好行凶慝，<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>谓之<span class=\"person\">浑沌</span>。",
        "[22.2] <span class=\"clan\">少暤氏</span>有不才子，毁信恶忠，崇饰恶言，<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>谓之<span class=\"person\">穷奇</span>。",
        "[22.3] <span class=\"clan\">颛顼氏</span>有不才子，不可教训，不知话言，<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>谓之<span class=\"person\">檮杌</span>。",
        "[22.4] 此三族世忧之。至于尧，尧未能去。",
        "[22.5] <span class=\"clan\">缙云氏</span>有不才子，贪于饮食，冒于货贿，<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>谓之<span class=\"person\">饕餮</span>。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c15",
      "id": "22.6",
      "indent": true,
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c15a",
        "html": "<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>恶之，比之<span class=\"person\">三凶</span>。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c15b",
        "from": "c15a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>宾於四门，乃流<span class=\"person\">四凶族</span>，迁于四裔，以御螭魅，於是四门辟，言毋凶人也。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "causal",
      "rid": "c16",
      "id": "23",
      "cause": {
        "rid": "c16a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>入于<span class=\"place\">大麓</span>，烈<span class=\"artifact\">风雷</span>雨不迷，<span class=\"person\">尧</span>乃知<span class=\"person\">舜</span>之足授<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>。"
      },
      "effect": {
        "rid": "c16b",
        "from": "c16a",
        "html": "<span class=\"person\">尧</span>老，使<span class=\"person\">舜</span>摄行<span class=\"official\">天子</span>政，<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>得举用事<span class=\"timeref\">二十年</span>，而<span class=\"person\">尧</span>使摄政。摄政<span class=\"timeref\">八年</span>而<span class=\"person\">尧</span>崩。<span class=\"timeref\">三年</span>丧毕，让<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>，<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>归<span class=\"person\">舜</span>。"
      }
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "23.1",
      "html": "而<span class=\"person\">禹</span>、<span class=\"person\">皋陶</span>、<span class=\"person\">契</span>、<span class=\"person\">后稷</span>、<span class=\"person\">伯夷</span>、<span class=\"person\">夔</span>、<span class=\"person\">龙</span>、<span class=\"person\">倕</span>、<span class=\"person\">益</span>、<span class=\"person\">彭祖</span>自<span class=\"person\">尧</span>时而皆举用，未有分职。於是<span class=\"person\">舜</span>乃至於<span class=\"place\">文祖</span>，谋于<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>，辟四门，明通四方耳目，命<span class=\"official\">十二牧</span>论帝德，行厚德，远佞人，则<span class=\"tribe\">蛮夷</span>率服。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "23.2",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>谓<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>曰：「有能奋庸美<span class=\"person\">尧</span>之事者，使居官相事？」"
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "[23.2.1] 皆曰：「<span class=\"person\">伯禹</span>为<span class=\"official\">司空</span>，可美帝功。」<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「嗟，然！<span class=\"person\">禹</span>，汝平水土，维是勉哉。」<span class=\"person\">禹</span>拜稽首，让於<span class=\"official\">稷</span>、<span class=\"person\">契</span>与<span class=\"person\">皋陶</span>。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「然，往矣。」",
        "[23.2.2] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">弃</span>，黎民始饥，汝<span class=\"person\">后稷</span>播时<span class=\"biology\">百穀</span>。」",
        "[23.2.3] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">契</span>，百姓不亲，<span class=\"concept\">五品</span>不驯，汝为<span class=\"official\">司徒</span>，而敬敷<span class=\"concept\">五教</span>，在宽。」",
        "[23.2.4] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">皋陶</span>，<span class=\"tribe\">蛮夷</span>猾夏，寇贼奸轨，汝作<span class=\"official\">士</span>，<span class=\"concept\">五刑</span>有服，<span class=\"concept\">五服</span>三就；五流有度，五度三居：维明能信。」",
        "[23.2.5] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「谁能驯予工？」皆曰<span class=\"person\">垂</span>可。於是以<span class=\"person\">垂</span>为<span class=\"person\">共工</span>。",
        "[23.2.6] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「谁能驯予上下<span class=\"biology\">草木</span><span class=\"biology\">鸟兽</span>？」皆曰<span class=\"person\">益</span>可。於是以<span class=\"person\">益</span>为<span class=\"official\">朕虞</span>。<span class=\"person\">益</span>拜稽首，让于诸臣<span class=\"person\">硃虎</span>、<span class=\"person\">熊罴</span>。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「往矣，汝谐。」遂以<span class=\"person\">硃虎</span>、<span class=\"person\">熊罴</span>为佐。",
        "[23.2.7] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「嗟！<span class=\"official\">四岳</span>，有能典朕<span class=\"concept\">三礼</span>？」皆曰<span class=\"person\">伯夷</span>可。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「嗟！<span class=\"person\">伯夷</span>，以汝为<span class=\"official\">秩宗</span>，夙夜维敬，直哉维静絜。」<span class=\"person\">伯夷</span>让<span class=\"person\">夔</span>、<span class=\"person\">龙</span>。",
        "[23.2.8] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「然。以<span class=\"person\">夔</span>为<span class=\"official\">典乐</span>，教稺子，直而温，宽而栗，刚而毋虐，简而毋傲；诗言意，歌长言，声依永，律和声，<span class=\"concept\">八音</span>能谐，毋相夺伦，<span class=\"mythical\">神人</span>以和。」<span class=\"person\">夔</span>曰：「於！予击石拊石，<span class=\"biology\">百兽</span>率舞。」",
        "[23.2.9] <span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「<span class=\"person\">龙</span>，朕畏忌谗说殄伪，振惊朕众，命汝为<span class=\"official\">纳言</span>，夙夜出入朕命，惟信。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "23.3",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>曰：「嗟！女二十有<span class=\"timeref\">二人</span>，敬哉，惟时相天事。」<span class=\"timeref\">三岁</span>一考功，三考绌陟，远近众功咸兴。分北<span class=\"tribe\">三苗</span>。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "24",
      "html": "此二十<span class=\"timeref\">二人</span>咸成厥功："
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "[24.1] <span class=\"person\">皋陶</span>为<span class=\"official\">大理</span>，平，民各伏得其实；",
        "[24.2] <span class=\"person\">伯夷</span>主礼，上下咸让；",
        "[24.3] <span class=\"person\">垂</span>主<span class=\"official\">工师</span>，百工致功；",
        "[24.4] <span class=\"person\">益</span>主<span class=\"official\">虞</span>，山泽辟；",
        "[24.5] <span class=\"person\">弃</span>主<span class=\"official\">稷</span>，<span class=\"biology\">百穀</span>时茂；",
        "[24.6] <span class=\"person\">契</span>主<span class=\"official\">司徒</span>，百姓亲和；",
        "[24.7] <span class=\"person\">龙</span>主宾客，远人至；",
        "[24.8] <span class=\"official\">十二牧</span>行而<span class=\"place\">九州</span>莫敢辟违；",
        "[24.9] 唯<span class=\"person\">禹</span>之功为大，披九山，通九泽，决<span class=\"place\">九河</span>，定<span class=\"place\">九州</span>，各以其职来贡，不失厥宜。方<span class=\"timeref\">五千里</span>，至于<span class=\"concept\">荒服</span>。南抚<span class=\"place\">交阯</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">北发</span>，<span class=\"tribe\">西戎</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">析枝</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">渠廋</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">氐</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">羌</span>，北<span class=\"tribe\">山戎</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">发</span>、<span class=\"tribe\">息慎</span>，东长、<span class=\"tribe\">鸟夷</span>，四<span class=\"place\">海</span>之内咸戴<span class=\"person\">帝舜</span>之功。於是<span class=\"person\">禹</span>乃兴九招之乐，致异物，<span class=\"biology\">凤皇</span>来翔。<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>明德皆自<span class=\"person\">虞帝</span>始。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "25",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span><span class=\"timeref\">年二十</span>以孝闻，<span class=\"timeref\">年三十</span><span class=\"person\">尧</span>举之，<span class=\"timeref\">年五十</span>摄行<span class=\"official\">天子</span>事，<span class=\"timeref\">年五十八</span><span class=\"person\">尧</span>崩，<span class=\"timeref\">年六十一</span>代尧践帝位。践帝位<span class=\"timeref\">三十九年</span>，南<span class=\"concept\">巡狩</span>，崩於<span class=\"place\">苍梧之野</span>。葬於<span class=\"place\">江南九疑</span>，是为<span class=\"place\">零陵</span>。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "25.1",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">舜</span>之践帝位，载<span class=\"official\">天子</span>旗，往朝父<span class=\"person\">瞽叟</span>，<span class=\"person\">夔</span><span class=\"person\">夔</span>唯谨，如子道。封弟<span class=\"person\">象</span>为诸侯。<span class=\"person\">舜</span>子<span class=\"person\">商均</span>亦不肖，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>乃豫荐<span class=\"person\">禹</span>於天。<span class=\"timeref\">十七年</span>而崩。<span class=\"timeref\">三年</span>丧毕，<span class=\"person\">禹</span>亦乃让<span class=\"person\">舜</span>子，如<span class=\"person\">舜</span>让<span class=\"person\">尧</span>子。诸侯归之，然後<span class=\"person\">禹</span>践<span class=\"official\">天子</span>位。"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "25.2",
      "html": "尧子<span class=\"person\">丹硃</span>，<span class=\"person\">舜</span>子<span class=\"person\">商均</span>，皆有疆土，以奉先祀。服其服，<span class=\"concept\">礼乐</span>如之。以客见<span class=\"official\">天子</span>，<span class=\"official\">天子</span>弗臣，示不敢专也。"
    },
    {
      "t": "hr"
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "总结：五帝世系"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "26",
      "html": "自<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>至<span class=\"person\">舜</span>、<span class=\"person\">禹</span>，皆同姓而异其国号，以章明德。"
    },
    {
      "t": "list",
      "indent": true,
      "items": [
        "故<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>为<span class=\"clan\">有熊</span>，",
        "<span class=\"person\">帝颛顼</span>为<span class=\"clan\">高阳</span>，",
        "<span class=\"person\">帝喾</span>为<span class=\"clan\">高辛</span>，",
        "<span class=\"person\">帝尧</span>为<span class=\"clan\">陶唐</span>，",
        "<span class=\"person\">帝舜</span>为<span class=\"clan\">有虞</span>。",
        "<span class=\"person\">帝禹</span>为<span class=\"clan\">夏后</span>而别氏，姓<span class=\"clan\">姒氏</span>。",
        "<span class=\"person\">契</span>为<span class=\"clan\">商</span>，姓<span class=\"clan\">子氏</span>。",
        "<span class=\"person\">弃</span>为<span class=\"clan\">周</span>，姓<span class=\"clan\">姬氏</span>。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "t": "hr"
    },
    {
      "t": "h2",
      "text": "太史公曰"
    },
    {
      "t": "p",
      "id": "27",
      "html": "<span class=\"person\">太史公</span>曰：学者多称<span class=\"clan\">五帝</span>，尚矣。然《尚书》独载<span class=\"person\">尧</span>以来；而<span class=\"concept\">百家</span>言<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>，其文不雅驯，荐绅先生难言之。<span class=\"person\">孔子</span>所传<span class=\"person\">宰予</span>问<span class=\"clan\">五帝</span>德及帝系姓，<span class=\"concept\">儒者</span>或不传。余尝西至<span class=\"place\">空桐</span>，北过<span class=\"place\">涿鹿</span>，东渐於<span class=\"place\">海</span>，南浮<span class=\"place\">江淮</span>矣，至长老皆各往往称<span class=\"person\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"person\">尧</span>、<span class=\"person\">舜</span>之处，风教固殊焉，总之不离古文者近是。予观《春秋》、《国语》，其<span class=\"tribe\">发</span>明<span class=\"clan\">五帝</span>德、帝系姓章矣，顾弟弗深考，其所表见皆不虚。书缺有间矣，其轶乃时时见於他说。非好学深思，心知其意，固难为浅见寡闻道也。余并论次，择其言尤雅者，故著为<span class=\"concept\">本纪</span>书首。"
    },
    {
      "t": "h3",
      "text": "赞"
    },
    {
      "t": "cite",
      "id": "28",
      "html": "帝出<span class=\"person\">少典</span>，居于<span class=\"place\">轩丘</span>。既代炎历，遂禽<span class=\"person\">蚩尤</span>。<span class=\"person\">高阳</span>嗣位，静深有谋。小大远近，莫不怀柔。爰洎<span class=\"person\">帝喾</span>，列圣同休。<span class=\"person\">帝挚</span>之弟，其号<span class=\"person\">放勋</span>。就之如日，望之如云。<span class=\"place\">郁夷</span>东作，<span class=\"place\">昧谷</span>西曛。明扬仄陋，玄德升闻。能让<span class=\"concept\">天下</span>，贤哉<span class=\"timeref\">二君</span>！"
    }
  ]
